    },
    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "What every writer wants",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 3.71,
      "endTime": 12.94,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "How do professional writers ignore what they were taught at school about writing?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 12.95,
      "endTime": 21.56,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "How",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "怎样，如何"
          },
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          },
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          },
          {
            "word": "School",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "学校"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "I have known very few writers,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 21.57,
      "endTime": 24.55,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Very",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "很，非常"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "but those I have known and whom I respect, confess at once that they have little idea where they are going when they first set pen to paper.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 24.56,
      "endTime": 36.12,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          },
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Pen",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "钢笔"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "They have a character, perhaps two;",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 36.13,
      "endTime": 39.09
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "they are in that condition of eager discomfort which passes for inspiration all admit radical changes of destination once the journey has begun;",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 39.1,
      "endTime": 50.65,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "one, to my certain knowledge, spent nine months on a novel about Kashmir,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 50.66,
      "endTime": 57.6,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "My",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "我的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "then reset the whole thing in the Scottish Highlands.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 57.61,
      "endTime": 61.37
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "I never heard of anyone making a 'skeleton', as we were taught at school.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 61.38,
      "endTime": 67.34,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          },
          {
            "word": "School",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "学校"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "In the breaking and remaking, in the timing interweaving, beginning afresh,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 67.35,
      "endTime": 74.79
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "the writer comes to discern things in his material which were not consciously in his mind when he began.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 74.8,
      "endTime": 82.82,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "This organic process, often leading to moments of extraordinary self-discovery, is of an indescribable fascination.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 82.83,
      "endTime": 94.31,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "A blurred image appears; he adds a brushstroke and another and it is gone",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 94.32,
      "endTime": 101.05,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "but something was there, and he will not rest till he has captured it.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 101.06,
      "endTime": 106.67,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Sometimes the yeast within a writer outlives a book he has written.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 106.68,
      "endTime": 112.76,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Book",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "书"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "I have heard of writers who read nothing but their own books;",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 112.77,
      "endTime": 117,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "like adolescents they stand before the mirror,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 117.01,
      "endTime": 120.45
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "and still cannot fathom the exact outline of the vision before them.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 120.46,
      "endTime": 126.14
    },
    {
      "id": "s16",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "For the same reason, writers talk interminably about their own books,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 126.15,
      "endTime": 132.36,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s17",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "winkling out hidden meanings, super-imposing new ones,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 132.37,
      "endTime": 137.18
    },
    {
      "id": "s18",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "begging response from those around them.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 137.19,
      "endTime": 140.56
    },
    {
      "id": "s19",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Of course a writer doing this is misunderstood: he might as well try to explain a crime or a love affair.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 140.57,
      "endTime": 148.14,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Well",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "健康的，良好的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s20",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "He is also, incidentally, an unforgivable bore.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 148.15,
      "endTime": 154.62,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s21",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "This temptation to cover the distance between himself and the reader,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 154.63,
      "endTime": 159.62,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s22",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "to study his image in the sight of those who do not know him, can be his undoing: he has begun to write to please.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 159.63,
      "endTime": 171.64,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Please",
            "pos": "int.",
            "meaning": "请"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s23",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "A young English writer made the pertinent observation a year or two back",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 171.65,
      "endTime": 176.84,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Young",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "年轻的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s24",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "that the talent goes into the first draft, and the art into the drafts that follow.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 176.85,
      "endTime": 183.59,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s25",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "For this reason also the writer, like any other artist,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 183.6,
      "endTime": 188.08,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s26",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "has no resting place, no crowd or movement in which he may take comfort,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 188.09,
      "endTime": 195.17,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s27",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "no judgment from outside which can replace the judgment from within.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 195.18,
      "endTime": 200.65,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s28",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "A writer makes order out of the anarchy of his heart;",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 200.66,
      "endTime": 204.69,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s29",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "he submits himself to a more ruthless discipline than any critic dreamed of,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 204.7,
      "endTime": 210.72
    },
    {
      "id": "s30",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "and when he flirts with fame, he is taking time off from living with himself,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 210.73,
      "endTime": 216.69,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s31",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "from the search for what his world contains at its inmost point.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 216.7,
      "endTime": 221.7,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          },
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}
